 *    - /@SF8#: set SF to 8
 *    - /@PL/H/M/x/X#: set power to Low, High or Max; extreme (PA_BOOST at +14dBm), eXtreme (PA_BOOST at +20dBm)
 *    - /@W34#: set sync word to 0x34
 *    - /@ON# or /@OFF#: power on/off the LoRa module
